Of course, I got you something.

06:10.292 --> 06:11.917
They're little rubies.

06:18.583 --> 06:19.542
Thank you.

06:20.333 --> 06:21.333
I love you.

06:27.333 --> 06:30.917
One at a time, please.
One at a time.

06:31.583 --> 06:35.417
Phone, beepers, knives, guns.
If it rings hand it.

06:36.125 --> 06:36.875
Hand over the phone, Edwin.

06:37.167 --> 06:39.458
- What phone? I'm clean.
- And the beeping is?

06:40.625 --> 06:42.042
- Thank you. Mr. Will.
- Mr. Jimmy.

06:42.458 --> 06:44.875
- Hey, are we still on for tonight?
- You're going down.

06:45.042 --> 06:46.125
Keep dreaming.

06:46.667 --> 06:48.333
Remember if your phone to school,
your parents...

06:48.625 --> 06:52.458
The expense of spirit in a waste
of shame is lust in action.

