I'm here to see Laura Gerard.
I'm her husband.

10:24.375 --> 10:26.917
Mr. Gerard, if you would follow me.

10:27.792 --> 10:29.917
I've been caring for your wife
ever since she came in.

10:30.625 --> 10:33.125
We've be keeping her pretty
sedated on pain medication.

10:46.208 --> 10:49.000
