internal bleeding.

10:49.458 --> 10:51.250
We're keeping a close watch on her.

10:53.750 --> 10:55.750
Lieutenant Richards, NOPD.

10:56.708 --> 10:57.792
She gave us description.

10:58.083 --> 11:00.792
