We're gonna get there.

11:03.750 --> 11:07.583
Could you all give me a moment
with my wife? Please?

11:33.875 --> 11:34.625
I'm sorry.

11:35.750 --> 11:36.792
I'm sorry.

11:39.125 --> 11:41.042
I wanted to her to come out with us.

11:41.750 --> 11:42.750
Hey, Will.

11:48.792 --> 11:49.708
I'm so sorry.

11:51.958 --> 11:54.083
The son of the bitch
who did this to Laura

11:54.792 --> 11:56.125
