11:58.250 --> 12:00.750
Go home, Jimmy. It's late.

12:01.417 --> 12:04.083
- I'll be all right.
- Anything you need, man, okay?

12:04.625 --> 12:06.875
- Anything. You just call me.
- Thanks.

12:18.333 --> 12:20.458
Close your own eyes. Tight.

12:23.750 --> 12:24.667
Thank you.

13:08.750 --> 13:10.625
I'm sorry to hear about your wife.

13:10.958 --> 13:12.208
Sounds terrible.

13:12.625 --> 13:15.292
Laura, right?
Is she okay?

13:16.792 --> 13:19.125
- Are you with the police?
- No.

13:19.625 --> 13:21.500
No, but I, um...

13:22.792 --> 13:25.875
a couple of years ago,
I experienced something similar.

13:26.458 --> 13:28.167
So it's probably
what you're going through right now.

13:28.458 --> 13:30.792
- You did?
- Yeah.

13:32.667 --> 13:34.625
The man who raped your wife,
he was, uh...

13:35.125 --> 13:37.625
he was paroled three weeks ago.

13:37.875 --> 13:39.333
You know who did this?

13:40.125 --> 13:42.625
He's done it before, he'll do it again.

13:43.292 --> 13:44.625
If you want...

13:46.625 --> 13:48.500
we can take care of him for you.

13:49.292 --> 13:52.500
Take care of who?
What do you mean arrest him?

13:52.958 --> 13:55.875
Uh, well, if we hand him
over to the police

13:56.333 --> 13:59.583
it'll take at least six months
for DNA tests to be completed.

13:59.958 --> 14:02.042
Ultimately there would be a trial
which your wife

14:02.583 --> 14:04.125
assuming she didn't drop
the charges would be...

14:04.417 --> 14:06.583
dragged through
this nightmare over and over.

14:06.792 --> 14:09.417
She'll be in court.
She'll be questioned by the lawyers.

14:10.458 --> 14:14.208
And even if the DA gets a conviction
which is not guaranteed

14:14.833 --> 14:17.625
the rapist can serve
as little as 11 months

14:18.125 --> 14:20.458
you know which is half the time
you get for tax evasion.

14:23.125 --> 14:24.250
Who are you?

14:25.917 --> 14:27.167
I'm Simon.

14:27.542 --> 14:30.292
I represent an organization that, uh...

14:30.792 --> 14:32.417
that deals with people.

14:33.250 --> 14:35.125
Like the man that raped your wife

14:35.583 --> 14:38.292
we would very much like
to take care of him for you.

14:40.208 --> 14:43.500
I really don't know
what you're talking about.

14:43.750 --> 14:45.583
You know what I'm talking about.

14:48.625 --> 14:50.417
This wouldn't cost you
anything financially.

14:50.625 --> 14:53.000
I mean if you did want us
to deal with this, uh

14:53.458 --> 14:56.292
we may ask a favor of you
at some point in the future.

14:56.667 --> 14:58.542
Look after somebody
for a couple of hours

14:58.708 --> 15:01.000
or break a security camera,
make a phone call or just

15:01.292 --> 15:03.292
something that would help us out.

15:09.625 --> 15:10.792
You...

15:11.958 --> 15:13.458
you know where he is?

15:13.792 --> 15:17.083
We do but we have a time issue
so, uh, we would have to...

15:17.417 --> 15:19.375
get an answer from you pretty quickly.

15:24.292 --> 15:25.458
Listen.

15:25.625 --> 15:30.417
We're just a few citizens
who are seeking justice.

15:32.083 --> 15:35.042
You know we love the city.
We're tired of watching it go to hell.

15:40.500 --> 15:41.542
No.

15:43.500 --> 15:44.583
No.

15:49.625 --> 15:53.792
Okay. That's okay.
You take care.

16:03.083 --> 16:04.125
Wait.

16:20.583 --> 16:24.625
There's a row of vending machines
in the Oncology Department cafeteria.

16:25.542 --> 16:28.625
If you want this to happen,
select the Forever Bar.

16:29.917 --> 16:34.000
Buy two of them, okay?
Two of them.

16:35.167 --> 16:37.750
And, Mr. Gerard, we never spoke.

16:38.625 --> 16:39.750
You never met me. Okay?

16:40.208 --> 16:42.917
You do not repeat
this conversation to anybody.

18:58.167 --> 19:00.750
- So, you got the healthy ones, huh?
- Excuse me?

19:01.292 --> 19:02.625
I just figured
if you're going to have a treat

19:02.875 --> 19:04.792
you should have
something that's worth it, huh?

20:52.250 --> 20:53.917
Hey. Cool, man.

20:54.458 --> 20:55.375
It's all right.

20:55.917 --> 20:56.792
What the fuck...?

20:57.875 --> 20:59.208
What do you want?

20:59.875 --> 21:01.458
You raped a woman tonight.

21:03.458 --> 21:04.708
Your wife?

21:06.292 --> 21:08.625
I have no wife.
I don't know who she is.

21:09.542 --> 21:12.958
My wife was murdered three months ago
by some scumbag just like you.

21:14.208 --> 21:16.458
Yeah. Yeah.

21:46.208 --> 21:47.500
Kirksey Funeral Homes.

21:48.167 --> 21:49.833
The hungry rabbit jumps.

21:50.125 --> 21:51.000
Mr. Gerard?

21:52.208 --> 21:54.292
- Mr. Gerard?
- Yes.

21:54.625 --> 21:57.167
We need you to sign a few more
insurance forms, please.

22:23.125 --> 22:25.458
I talked to the police this morning.

22:26.417 --> 22:29.375
They found the rapist.

22:34.958 --> 22:36.292
He's dead.

22:37.458 --> 22:39.458
Committed suicide.

23:34.625 --> 23:36.875
We'll find a way to get over this

23:37.583 --> 23:39.000
together.

23:39.958 --> 23:41.208
I know.

23:42.708 --> 23:44.958
- I'm sorry.
- No.

23:45.625 --> 23:47.167
Don't say that.

23:48.500 --> 23:49.875
It's just hard.

23:54.000 --> 23:56.500
Sweetheart, that man is gone.

24:01.000 --> 24:03.333
- I want a new lock on the door.
- Okay.

24:03.667 --> 24:05.083
And bars on the windows.

24:34.375 --> 24:35.458
Will?

24:35.833 --> 24:37.125
Yeah, just me.

24:37.583 --> 24:39.625
- Did you lock the door?
- Doors locked.

24:44.917 --> 24:46.542
I sound like a crazy person.

24:46.875 --> 24:50.125
No, you sound like a person
who's getting over something difficult.

24:56.042 --> 24:57.083
I wanna buy a gun.

24:59.958 --> 25:03.792
We're not keeping a gun in this house.
No guns.

25:09.000 --> 25:12.292
All right. If your stance is not stable
you're not gonna be stable.

25:12.958 --> 25:15.917
Remember feet shoulder-width apart
knees slightly bent.

25:16.792 --> 25:18.125
Lean forward at the waist.

25:18.583 --> 25:19.833
Bring the gun to your eyesight.

25:20.792 --> 25:22.750
You got that front sight, rear sight.

25:23.042 --> 25:24.583
