25:26.625 --> 25:27.958
There's your pepper spray.

25:29.208 --> 25:31.375
Remember, squeeze the trigger.

25:31.958 --> 25:33.375
- Take care.
- Thanks.

25:33.958 --> 25:35.917
Oh, on you I missed.

25:36.875 --> 25:39.583
- Well, you still have to make it.
- All right,

25:39.958 --> 25:41.958
- side pocket.
- Oh, no. A lot of green, Laura.

25:42.167 --> 25:43.417
A lot of green.

25:46.375 --> 25:49.042
- Oh, good game, honey.
- You're a pool shark.

25:50.417 --> 25:51.000
You noticed.

25:51.333 --> 25:53.500
All right, let's go again.
I'll give you a chance to even the score.

25:53.833 --> 25:57.125
- All right, I'll rack 'em, you grab drinks.
- Fine. Good idea.

26:07.458 --> 26:08.000
Hello?

26:08.458 --> 26:11.083
Will? Come outside.
I need to talk to you.

26:11.458 --> 26:13.958
- Who is this?
- It's Simon. I have to talk to you.

26:14.458 --> 26:15.583
Come outside.

26:15.875 --> 26:17.833
Just tell Laura, it's your sister.

26:21.375 --> 26:24.167
- Hello?
- You see the store on the corner?

26:25.417 --> 26:27.500
- Yes.
- Go in there.

26:33.583 --> 26:35.208
Now I want you to buy a pack of gum

26:35.958 --> 26:37.833
then come out the back entrance.

26:39.417 --> 26:40.917
- Have any gum?
- Yes.

26:41.375 --> 26:42.917
- How much is it?
- Dollar fifty.

26:44.833 --> 26:47.083
- Is that the back entrance?
- Yeah, through that.

27:01.792 --> 27:03.917
- Hey, Will, come on in.
- What do you want?

27:04.542 --> 27:07.083
Just a quick talk.
Relax. You're looking good.

27:07.500 --> 27:10.083
So is your wife. I'm glad to
see you guys are back on track.

27:10.417 --> 27:11.917
What do you want to talk about?

27:12.958 --> 27:14.083
What do you think?

27:21.208 --> 27:24.917
There is a, uh, mailbox
at the entrance of the zoo.

27:25.625 --> 27:27.667
And we would like you
to go there tomorrow after work

27:27.875 --> 27:30.792
and mail this at exactly 4:15.

27:33.875 --> 27:35.292
What is it?

27:35.625 --> 27:37.167
It's a letter to Santa Claus.

27:38.292 --> 27:39.333
Santa Claus?

27:41.917 --> 27:43.708
- And then I'm even?
- Well, that's not up to me.

27:44.125 --> 27:45.583
Well, who's it up to?

27:45.917 --> 27:49.625
All I know is I need you to mail that

28:01.625 --> 28:02.042
Where did you go?

28:02.250 --> 28:05.667
Well, my sister called. It was too noisy
in here so I had to step outside.

28:07.792 --> 28:09.792
- Are you okay?
- Yeah, everything's fine.

28:10.792 --> 28:11.708
- Fine.
- Play again? Double or nothing?

28:12.042 --> 28:13.750
No. I'm real tired. Let's go.

28:14.667 --> 28:15.958
- Okay?
- Okay.

29:20.292 --> 29:20.833
Yes?

29:21.583 --> 29:23.167
- You're in the mailbox?
- I am.

29:23.667 --> 29:24.958
Open the letter.

29:25.917 --> 29:27.792
Okay. Hold on.

29:39.708 --> 29:40.833
- Okay.
- Go to the zoo.

29:41.292 --> 29:43.417
Pay for the ticket with cash
and wait by the entrance.

29:44.125 --> 29:45.625
If the woman and the girls show up,

29:46.125 --> 29:51.000
you follow them. If that man appears,
and say, "The hungry rabbit jumps."

29:51.542 --> 29:54.083
- You got it?
- The hungry rabbit jumps.

29:54.750 --> 29:55.917
That's right.

29:56.417 --> 29:59.083
- What does it mean?
- It means what it means.

29:59.417 --> 30:02.167
Now, memorize the number
and their pictures

30:02.458 --> 30:04.542
and tear up that sheet
until it's confetti.

30:05.917 --> 30:07.000
You got it?

30:07.875 --> 30:09.083
Okay, good luck.

30:35.583 --> 30:37.958
I wanna welcome you to the zoo
and to our elephant show.

30:38.167 --> 30:41.958
We have two elephants here
in the Audobon Zoo both Asian females.

30:42.417 --> 30:43.500
This is Jean.

30:44.042 --> 30:45.583
She is 36 years old

30:46.042 --> 30:48.250
and she weighs 7600 pounds.

30:49.625 --> 30:53.500
Anya is 45
and she's 10,400 pounds.

30:54.667 --> 30:55.625
What we're gonna show you today
are a few behaviors

30:55.958 --> 30:57.458
that the elephants know

30:57.875 --> 31:00.083
and things that we need
to do daily to take a look at 'em

31:00.500 --> 31:02.542
to make sure they're healthy
and doing well.

31:22.625 --> 31:23.708
What you're looking at?
I've seen bitch.

31:23.958 --> 31:26.208
All right! All right.
Nobody's looking at anybody.

31:26.458 --> 31:28.458
- Settle down. Come on.
- Don't touch me.

31:28.625 --> 31:30.583
I'm not touching you, I'm guiding you.

31:31.458 --> 31:33.500
All right. We need everybody to...

31:41.083 --> 31:43.666
- Hey, Will.
- You came into my classroom?

31:44.500 --> 31:48.500
- Why? I don't get this.
- No need to shout, Will. I'm right here.

31:51.791 --> 31:53.250
I've done everything you asked

31:53.625 --> 31:56.500
- the Santa Claus letter, the zoo...
- The man didn't show up?

31:56.791 --> 31:59.250
No, I don't think so but,
look, I'm finished.

31:59.458 --> 32:01.750
Will, you've been very helpful
and we appreciate it.

32:02.000 --> 32:03.416
But what you've done
is only part of it, okay?

32:03.625 --> 32:06.416
- We just need you to do one more thing.
- I think you made a mistake here.

32:06.791 --> 32:09.375
I'm not cut out to the kind of activity.

32:09.708 --> 32:11.250
- Yeah?
- I hope you're right.

32:11.458 --> 32:14.583
Will, a promise is a promise, okay?
I'll be in touch.

32:23.750 --> 32:25.416
- Oh.
- Excuse me. Hey, now, my bad, brother.

32:25.625 --> 32:27.166
- It's all right.
- Oh.

32:27.958 --> 32:29.791
- You dropped something.
- No, it's not mine.

32:30.125 --> 32:31.458
Oh, sure it is.

32:32.541 --> 32:34.916
Hey, this isn't mine.

33:12.375 --> 33:13.416
- Will?
- Yeah?

33:13.958 --> 33:16.708
We finished rehearsal early today.
You wanna go out for dinner?

